caller_intent: The caller needs assistance but the intended recipient (a female colleague) is unavailable until 10:30 AM. The caller insists on resolving the matter today.
resolution_steps: Agent confirms the recipient is in a meeting until 10:30 AM.
Agent offers to have the recipient call the caller back after the meeting.
Caller agrees and provides their phone number (336-817-1873).
Agent confirms they will relay the message and arrange the callback.
summary: A caller reached out for assistance, but the intended recipient was unavailable until 10:30 AM. The agent arranged for the recipient to call back after the meeting. The caller emphasized the need for immediate resolution, and the agent confirmed they would relay the message.
